OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice?
OL,6,FStudents and parents in Reading are
OL,7,Fbeing urged to remain vigilant for the
OL,8,Fsigns of meningitis and sepsis,
OL,9,Ffollowing an outbreak in the Berkshire
OL,10,Ftown.
OL,12,FOne teenager has died, and two others
OL,13,Fare in hospital following an outbreak
OL,14,Fof the "invasive" disease in the area.
OL,16,FPeople who are unwell should call NHS
OL,17,F111 or their GP, or if they are
OL,18,Fseriously unwell, go to their nearest
OL,19,FEmergency Department.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
