OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice?
OL,6,FAntibiotics are being offered to
OL,7,Fpeople who have come into close
OL,8,Fcontact with those who have tested
OL,9,Fpositive for the disease.
OL,11,FWhat is meningitis and what causes it?
OL,13,FMeningitis is an infection of the
OL,14,Fprotective membranes that surround the
OL,15,Fbrain and spinal cord. It is usually
OL,16,Fcaused by a bacterial or viral
OL,17,Finfection. Bacterial meningitis is
OL,18,Frarer but more serious than viral
OL,19,Fmeningitis.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
