OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice?
OL,6,FIt can affect anyone but is more
OL,7,Fcommon in babies, children, teenagers
OL,8,Fand young adults.
OL,10,FMeningitis can be very serious if not
OL,11,Ftreated quickly, and can lead to life-
OL,12,Fthreatening sepsis and permanent
OL,13,Fdamage to the brain or nerves.
OL,15,FWhat are the symptoms of meningitis or
OL,16,Fsepsis?
OL,18,FThey can include:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
