OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice?
OL,6,FPatients may need to stay in hospital
OL,7,Ffor a few days or weeks.
OL,9,FIn cases of mild meningitis, patients
OL,10,Fmay be sent home if tests confirm it
OL,11,Fis viral, which usually gets better on
OL,12,Fits own. Most patients start to feel
OL,13,Fbetter within seven to 10 days.
OL,15,FBut severe viral meningitis may also
OL,16,Fbe treated in hospital.
OL,18,FWhat should you do if you think you
OL,19,Fhave meningitis?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
