OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1778854269
OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice?
OL,6,FThe NHS recommends that people call
OL,7,F999 for an ambulance or go to their
OL,8,Fnearest A&E.
OL,10,FPeople are advised to trust their
OL,11,Finstincts, as someone with meningitis
OL,12,For sepsis can get a lot worse very
OL,13,Fquickly.
